headline: Jack Henry & Associates速 Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc.速 (NASDAQ: JKHY) today announced its Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $.58 per share. The cash dividend on its common stock, par value $.01 per share, is payable on September 26, 2025, to stockholders of record as of September 5, 2025.
